{"tid":1538660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事實：一係港共倒台, 一係我地萬劫不復","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:06:42.000Z","uid":124859,"like":93,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2268d82adbe2bc8358133de0c0c916169eea8b85","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撤回當無事發生？已經唔可能。<br />\n事到如今, 港共欠左我地太多<br />\n我地點對得住死左既手足，被捕既手足，台灣流亡既義士？<br />\n依家只有拉倒港共支爆，一係我地萬劫不復，永無翻身之日，大清算。<br />\n唔係港共死就我地亡<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n９月８日見</span>"},{"pid":"524617b01088f78ae304c858901535813148e61d","tid":1538660,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176e98fc2c0b74326aa3b4957eb90921763155e8","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"港共講咩都唔好信，唔好收貨"},{"pid":"0fde735a0939f0290fe9ed330fed716b0002e4eb","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf46c224e77b02e8f353930ae4bc44e568ab54c8","tid":1538660,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"中共不倒 港共不滅"},{"pid":"c8a69ddd55e6c346eeb4e0133362d1822c2fede5","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf46c224e77b02e8f353930ae4bc44e568ab54c8","tid":1538660,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"中共不倒 港共不滅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6397a29a4595361e3223bb71362504d0f1a095","tid":1538660,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"消息話除咗撤回仲會搞個真相委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如抗爭者撤回法案換成解散警犬隊，5-1+1=5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續五大訴求，Business as usual！<br />\n繼續保持呢場運動嘅熱度， 盡量縮短政府撤回法案引起嘅運動低潮期。<br />\n同時狗隻士氣被林病所設嘅真相委員會 打擊，陷入低谷。<br />\n堅持落去，政府就會兵敗如山倒。<br />\n邊個嗌收工 嗌停 就係有錢佬隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e986ad5062aea9da011f4584e2dbf75a37e4be0a","tid":1538660,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"一句講曬《冇雙真普選 就等被清算》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"05656f86fb6f0efc2f72f5cf0e18b12bc5a7b94c","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc2ce0f92ca146d7052332a278c4a5f3a627f20","tid":1538660,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"8cc6da1c056711bc485f94b35f45bd1ea4d55494","tid":1538660,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3c799a7ee26dbfa754d4401641d7644bb3bdbdb2","tid":1538660,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div>"},{"pid":"88ca53ecb33726ea41ec24a575abc4338b766824","tid":1538660,"uid":183108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"大家記住，邊撚個講過話秋後算賬！"},{"pid":"9a19c81149ac7d759f0f57d5b4ba3c76d543a2d7","tid":1538660,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"［幫手推］隔離熱門po話撤回條例會令下次遊行失去一大班和理非喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14a462c263e9bb44e9600991b23fe485a0c76a46","tid":1538660,"uid":34088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4db40573f952c981866197b3ca501819f011250","tid":1538660,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d9a277e9e18cf1701ae6b7ea9390ef2619eb17","tid":1538660,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"101d8aa66bbf0121231c471460d56e17d38553a7","tid":1538660,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7e7bf930617a5990c578a4243a72b97fae832a","tid":1538660,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a8763e9f50a251d29f1131717a9209dd175cf9","tid":1538660,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"<i